EOW2
The fountain is running smoothly with clear water. In its center is a tall statue of a helmed woman holding a staff and shield. It reminds you of the soldier statue in the ruined courtyard fountain. Now that you think about it, it's the same fountain.
Now is NOT the time for a swim, though it's tempting. You don't even have a change of clothes, and you aren't wearing servant's garb.
An interesting but far-fetched proposition.
Peering into the water-filled basin...